AVR-libc library for a LCD with HD44780 display controller for AVR 8-bit microcontrollers.
The library implements 4-bit bus for communication with the LCD.
Config.h header is used to define the microcontroller PINs for the LCD bus.
Tested on Atmel Atmega32 microcontroller.

